 The musician who hardly ever comments on his personal life and only revealed that he was officially off the market last year has confirmed to TshisaLIVE that he is a father-to be. I wouldn t have liked to share you know I am a conservative man and I keep my personal life private but yes I am expecting a baby he said.Nathi was only willing to confirm the news but would not divulge any further details about his wife s pregnancy only saying he is grateful for the blessing.Daily Sun reports that a source close to Nathi claims Nathi s wife is heavily pregnant and would be giving birth sometime in July.